AWS S3 (Simple Storage Service)
--------------------------------------
-------------------------------------
AWS S3 is a cloud object storage service provided by Amazon. It is more reliable, scalable, and secure than traditional than on-premises storage systems. 
Important Features of S3 :-
1) Storage classes
2) Lifecycle management
3) Versioning
 
 ---- Storage classes                                      First byte latency
    1) S3 Standard                                              miliseconds
    2) S3 Standard - IA (Infrequent Access)                     miliseconds
    3) S3 One Zone- IA (Infrequent Access)                      miliseconds
    4) S3 Intelligent Tiering                                   miliseconds
    5) S3 Glacier Instant Retrival                              miliseconds
    6) S3 Glacier Flexible Retrival                             minutes -- hours
    7) S3 Glaricer Deep Archive                                     hours
    
    
